EmailTemplate.subject: AML and CTF event this December
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Contact.FirstName}
Compliance Week is hosting a one day event on Anti Money Laundering and Counter Terrorism Financing Compliance. I wanted to check in to see if {!Account.Name} would be interested in sponsorship.
I've listed below some more details about the event.
Compliance Week Conversation on AML and CTF Compliance:
One day event held on December 5th in New York at the Princeton Club. This in-depth conversation allows senior compliance, finance, and audit executives the opportunity to discuss ways to mitigate risk in the ever-changing world of anti-money laundering and counter terrorism financing. Each topic will be introduced by a panel of expert speakers followed by audience participation. After lunch round-table discussions allow for best practice sharing by industry. Space in the room is limited to 75. The event will be co-hosted by Compliance Week and Financial Research Associates (a sister company of Compliance Week who specializes in financial events). FRA will organize the event, and Compliance Week will host, promote and work with the sponsors. http://events.complianceweek.com/AML2016
Attending the event will be 75 corporate legal, compliance, audit, AML, and KYC executives from global public companies with the majority from financial services. The preliminary agenda is attached. The event will look at issues such as the top AML & CTF risks, enforcement, global trends, strategies, red flags and best practices.
We are looking for three sponsors. There is one level of sponsorship which includes a speaking position on a panel session; you can moderate or participate as a panelist.
Presenting Sponsorship: $8,500
Panel speaking role with ability to help identify the other panelists
Ad in electronic brochure
250 word profile on brochure
Logo and hyperlink on website
Attendee list 30 days prior (then weekly thru the event)
Customized pre-conference email blast to 52k Compliance Week users (rate card for the email is $5k)
Listed on signage and on all promotional materials
Exhibit display table
Luncheon, breakfast or lanyard sponsor
2 conference passes
Please let me know if you have questions or would like to discuss. I look forward to hearing from you,
Kind Regards,
Julie Van Gelder, Advertising and Sponsorship Sales
P: 617.570.8612 |C: 978.758.6098
